sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server
    
    browser->>server: GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/spa
    activate server
    server-->>browser: HTML document
    NOTE: there is a change to how the form tag is written, there is a preventDefault, so that the page doesn't get reloaded, and that input is not automatically submitted to the server
    NOTE: however, with the onsubmit handler, in this case, the input is still submitted to the server
    deactivate server
    
    browser->>server: GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/main.css
    activate server
    server-->>browser: the css file
    deactivate server
    
    browser->>server: GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/main.js
    activate server
    server-->>browser: the JavaScript file
    NOTE: the linked js file is different, with empty tags to be filled dynamically
    deactivate server
    
    Note right of browser: The browser starts executing the JavaScript code that fetches the JSON from the server
    
    browser->>server: GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/data.json
    activate server
    server-->>browser: [{ "content": "HTML is easy", "date": "2023-1-1" }, ... ]
    deactivate server

    Note right of browser: The browser executes the callback function that renders the notes